         <p>The status of copyright in the unpublished writings of Albert James Myer is governed by
            the Copyright Law of the United States (Title 17, U.S.C.).</p>
      </userestrict>
      <accessrestrict encodinganalog="506 0">
         <head>Access and Restrictions</head>
         <p>The papers of Albert James Myer are open to research. Researchers are advised to contact
            the Manuscript Reading Room prior to visiting. Many collections are stored off-site and
            advance notice is needed to retrieve these items for research use.</p>
      </accessrestrict>
      <altformavail encodinganalog="530">
